name: Quality cushion inserts - eco poly, feather & foam or feather (assorted sizes)
description:
Soft and cuddly or firm and feathery. The choice is yours!
Putting the finishing touches to a room? Don't forget your cushion inserts.

Available in many sizes (see drop down menu)

In either of the following fill options:-

Eco-poly inserts - these soft fill inserts are made from recycled plastic bottles! recycled PET fiber is derived from 100% post consumer water bottles. The fiber looks, feels and performs in the same way as a high-grade poly fiber, but is completely recycled. For every 1kg of fiber used, we save around 70 water bottles from ending up in landfill. Our Recycled PET fiber is also 100% non-allergenic - great for the environment & good for you!

Or feather and foam - made from crumbed foam & duck feathers these give a firmer feel & will last much longer than the poly fill. 

Feather inserts are the timeless classic - they last a long time, are covered in a tightly woven japara fabric which stops the feathers poking through & when they get a little flat just "poof" them up!

name: 'The journey of the bee' candles- asstd scents
description:
"The men of experiment are like the ant; they only collect and use. But the bee...gathers its materials from the flowers of the garden and of the field, but transforms and digests it by a power of its own." ~ Leonardo da Vinci 
In celebration of the bee, this collection represents the stops on the journey to pollinate. Bold colors and modern packaging compliment the crisp natural fragrances of our Journey of the Bee Collection. 

A rich bee's wax blend poured into a 5.5oz matte black glass, with an approx burning time of 45 hours.

Available in-
ROSE
"Peace is the interlude between two wars. You have no rose without a thorn; the diligent picker will avoid the pricks and gather the flower. There is no bee without the sting; cleverness consists in gathering the honey nevertheless."

~ Sri Sathya Sai Baba

Enjoy the fragrance of a lush Rose Garden with this Rose scented beeswax.

RAW HONEY
"For the rest, whatever we have got has been by infinite labor, and search, and ranging through every corner of nature; the difference is that instead of dirt and poison, we have rather chosen to fill our hives with honey and wax, thus furnishing mankind with the two noblest of things, which are sweetness and light."

~ Jonathan Swift

Indulge in natural sweetness with the warm glow of the Raw Honey scented beeswax.

WILD BLACKBERRY
"Let us draw a lesson from nature, which always works by short ways. When the fruit is ripe, it falls."

~ Ralph Waldo Emmerson

There is no need to patiently wait for the fruit to ripen. Enjoy the natural sweet scent of late summer's dark and ripe fruit with our intoxicating Wild Blackberry scented beeswax

FREESIA
"Sweet springtime is my time is your time is our time for springtime is love time and viva sweet love."

~ e.e. cummings

Live sweet love all year long with our sweet and fresh Freesia.

CLOVER
"The pedigree of honey does not concern the bee; A clover, any time, to him Is aristocracy."

~ Emily Dickinson

Take in our Clover scented beeswax, and imagine strolling across your kingdom's clover fields. 

ORANGE BLOSSOM
"Well, I'm goin down to Florida and get some sand in my shoes Or maybe California and get some sand in my shoes I'll ride that Orange Blossom Special and lose these New York blues."

~ Johnny Cash Orange Blossom Special

Lose your New York blues with crisp and clean fragrance of our Orange Blossom scented beeswax. 

All are in stock and ready to ship NOW!

RRP $34.95

name: Indian Block printed Tablecloth 180cm square 100% cotton (Assorted designs)
description:
The traditional Indian art form of hand block printing is used in the creation of these beautiful tablecloths

Many of the motifs are inspired by nature - flowers, leaves, birds, vegetables, fish and seashells, making them an elegant addition to your home.
Print colours are freshly mixed each day by the colour master in charge of each print workshop.
The printer then dips the wooden block into a custom-mixed tray of fresh dye which is placed on top of a small table on castors and moves down the length of the cloth stamping with skillful precision. Making each one unique.

Made from 100% cotton
Measurements- 180 x 180cm

Available in Fig. green and white flower and white on white

RRP $79.90
